query_text:
SELECT DISTINCT ON (campaign_id, group_id, wave_id, action_id)
    campaign_id, cm_group_id AS group_id, wave_id, action_id, action_entity_id
FROM concatYtTablesRange('//home/logfeller/logs/taxi-crm-hub-experiments/stream/5min', '2022-04-05 12:00:00', '2022-04-07 12:00:00')
WHERE action_type = 'COMMUNICATION' AND status == 'SUCCESS'
GROUP BY campaign_id, group_id, wave_id, action_id, action_entity_id
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY campaign_id, group_id, wave_id, action_id
LIMIT 10;
